div.p:
In the realm of new ideas, the group thought we should examine these
                            areas: 

—speeding up a satellite communications system for Latin
                                    America;

—help in promoting educational TV;

—development of research libraries on microfilm;

—cooperation in development of “food from sea”
                                    resources;

—development of protein concentrates for child-feeding
                                    programs; and

—computerized access to information, perhaps drawing on NIH’s
                                    development of an electronic library in medicine.
